Project Dependency Graph

Dependency Tree

  • org.kew.rmf:string-transformers:jar:0.2.1
    String Transformers

    Description: This is a collection of string transformers, all of which implement a “transform” method that takes a string and returns one. Some transformers are very generic, and others are aimed at botany, taxonomy or related literature.

    URL: https://github.com/RBGKew/String-Transformers

    Project License: MIT license
